Package uk.ac.diamond.powder_toolkit.dataAnalysis

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPowderIndexer
    Interface designed to be a wrapper for indexing algorithms
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPowderIndexer
    Abstract class used to create an indexing wrapper
    Comparator
    Comparator is a class designed to compare arrays, it is a conversion from an original python script and its main use should be the comparison of large datasets eg Intensity's
    LoadedDataObject
    Loaded Data object is an object used to store all data in the program
    Loader
    Loader Class designed to load in the data easily, it uses loader factory and a makes basic decisions about the files (is it a .nxs) for example
    MyDataHolder
    Data holder is a list of dataobbjects used to hold all data in the program
    Ntreor
    Ntreor indexing wrapper, all new indexing programs should have structure similar to this
    ServiceLoader
    OSGI services
